\c 11
\p
\v 1 Iniwo mugore rekutanga raDhariyasi muMedhiya, ndakasimuka kusimbisa nekumutsigira.
\s Hondo dzeVaPeresia neVaGiriki
\p
\v 2 Ikozvinowo ndava kuzokuudza chokwadi. Tarira, kuchamira amwe madzimambo matatu paPeresia; uye wechina achava mupfumi pane vese; uye paachava nesimba kubudikidza neufumi hwake achamutsa vese kupikisa umambo hweGirisi.
\v 3 Zvino mambo ane simba achasimuka, uye achatonga nekutonga kukuru, nekuita zvinoenderana nechido chake.
\v 4 Zvino paachasimuka, umambo hwake huchagurwa, uye huchaparadzanisirwa kumhepo ina dzekumatenga, uye kwete kukubudirira kwake, uye zvisingaenderani nekutonga kwake kwaakatonga; nokuti umambo hwake huchadzurirwa vamwewo kunze kweava.
\p
\v 5 Zvino mambo wekuchamhembe achava nesimba, ne\add umwe\add* wemachinda ake; zvino \add iye\add* achava nesimba kumupfuura, zvino achatonga; kutonga kwake kuchava kutonga kukuru.
\v 6 Zvino pakupera kwemakore, vachabatana, nokuti mukunda wamambo wekuchamhembe achaenda kuna mambo wekumaodzanyemba kunoita dzakaenzaniswa; asi haangarambi akabata simba reruoko; uye haangamiri, kana ruoko rwake; asi \add mukunda\add* achapiwa, nevakamuunza, newakamubereka, newakamusimbisa panguva idzi.
\v 7 Asi kuchasimuka \add umwe\add* kubva padavi remidzi yake \add pa\add*chinzvimbo chake; uye achauya nehondo, uye achapinda munhare dzamambo wekumaodzanyemba, uye achabata nekuvarwisa ndokukunda.
\v 8 Nevamwari vavo pamwe nemachinda avo pamwe nemidziyo yavo inokosha yesirivha neyegoridhe achatapira kuEgipita; iyewe achaenderera kwe\add amwe\add* makore kupfuura mambo wekumaodzanyemba.
\v 9 Naizvozvo mambo wekuchamhembe achapinda paumambo ndokudzokera kunyika yake.
\p
\v 10 Asi vanakomana vake vachaenda kunorwa, uye vachaunganidza chaunga chevarwi vakuru. Zvino achauya zvirokwazvo, ndokufashamira, ndokupfuura, ipapo achadzoka ndokuenda kunorwa, kusvika kunhare yake.
\v 11 Zvino mambo wekuchamhembe achatsamwa zvikuru, ndokubuda ndokurwa naye, namambo wekumaodzanyemba; iye achamutsa chaunga chikuru, asi chaunga ichi chichapiwa muruoko rwake.
\v 12 Chaunga chichinge chabviswa, moyo wake uchazvikudza; uye achawisira pasi vane makumi ezvuru, asi haangavi nesimba.
\v 13 Nokuti mambo wekumaodzanyemba achadzoka, zvino achamisa chaunga chakakura pane chekutanga, uye pakupera kwenguva dzemakore achasvika zvirokwazvo ane hondo huru nenhumbi zhinji.
\p
\v 14 Zvino panguva idzodzo kuchasimuka vazhinji kurwisa mambo wekuchamhembe; uye vane hasha vevanhu vako vachazvikudza kuti vasimbise chiratidzo, asi vachagumburwa.
\v 15 Naizvozvo mambo wekumaodzanyemba achasvika, ndokututa murwi, ndokutapa guta rakashoshewa kwazvo; uye maoko ekuchamhembe haangamiri, nevanhu vake vakasarudzwa; uye hakungavi nesimba rekumira.
\v 16 Asi uyo anouya kumurwisa achaita zvinoenderana nechido chake; uye hakuna angamira pamberi pake; uye achamira panyika yakaisvonaka, uye kuparadzwa kuchava muruoko rwake.
\v 17 Zvino acharinzira chiso chake kupinda nesimba reumambo hwake hwese, nevakarurama vanaye, achaita saizvozvo; uye achamupa mukunda wemukadzi kuti amuparadze; asi haangamiri, haangavi wake.
\v 18 Uye achatendeusira chiso chake kuzviwi, zvino achatora vazhinji; asi muchinda achagumisa kushoorwa kwake kwaari, kunze kwekuti achadzosera kushoorwa kwake kwaari.
\v 19 Zvino acharinzira chiso chake kunhare dzenyika yekwake; asi achagumburwa ndokuwa, ndokusawanikwa.
\p
\v 20 Zvino pachinzvimbo chake pachasimuka \add umwe\add* achaita kuti mukwiridzi wemutero apfuure \add pa\add*kubwinya kweumambo, asi mukati memazuva mashoma achaparadzwa, pasina kutsamwa kukuru, uye pasina hondo.
\v 21 Zvino pachasimuka pachinzvimbo chake anoshoreka, wavasingazopi rukudzo rweumambo; asi achapinda parugare ndokutora umambo nemashoko ekubata kumeso.
\v 22 Zvino maoko efashame vachayeredzwa kubva pamberi pake, uye vachagurwa, hongu nemuchinda wesungano.
\v 23 Zvino pashure pekusungana naye achabata nekunyengera, nokuti achakwira ndokuva ane simba ane rudzi rudiki.
\v 24 Achapinda parugare kunyange nepamusoro penzvimbo dzakaorera dzedunhu; zvino achaita zvisina kumboitwa nemadzibaba ake uye madzibaba emadzibaba ake zvavasina kumboita; achaparadzira pakati pavo zvakajimbiwa, zvakapambiwa, nefuma zhinji. Zvino achanangisa mano ake pamusoro penhare, asi kusvika yava nguva.
\v 25 Zvino achamutsa simba rake nemoyo wake kurwisa mambo wekuchamhembe nehondo huru. Zvino mambo wekuchamhembe achamutsirwa kurwa nehondo huru uye ine simba, asi haangamiri, nokuti varonga mazano kumurwisa.
\v 26 Hongu, vanodya mugove wake wekudya vachamuparadza, nehondo yake ichayeredza, uye vazhinji vachawa vaurawa.
\v 27 Zvino moyo yemadzimambo awa maviri iri pane zvakaipa, uye vachataura nhema patafura imwe, asi hazvingabudiriri, nokuti kuguma kuchavapo panguva yakatarwa.
\v 28 Zvino achadzokera kunyika yake nefuma zhinji, nemoyo wake uchapikisa sungano tsvene, zvino achaita ndokudzokera kunyika yake.
\p
\v 29 Panguva yakatarwa achadzokera, ndokuuya akananga kunyika yekuchamhembe; asi hazvingavi sepakutanga kana sepakupedzisira.
\v 30 Nokuti zvikepe zveKitimi zvichauya kumurwisa; naizvozvo achaora mwoyo, ndokudzoka ndokutsamwa pamusoro pesungano tsvene, ndokuita ndokudzokera. Zvino achava nehanya nevakasiya sungano tsvene.
\v 31 Zvino maoko achamira kurutivi rwake, uye vachasvibisa nzvimbo tsvene yesimba, uye vachabvisa chibairo chezuva nezuva, ndokumisa chinyangadzo chinoparadza.
\v 32 Nevanoitira sungano zvakaipa achavasvibisa nemashoko ekubata kumeso; asi vanhu vanoziva Mwari wavo vachava vakasimba, uye vachaita.
\v 33 Zvino vanonzwisisa pakati pevanhu vachadzidzisa vazhinji; asi vachawa nemunondo, uye nemurazvo wemoto, neutapwa, uye nekupambiwa mazuva \add mazhinji\add*.
\v 34 Zvino pavanenge vachiwa, vachabatsirwa nerubatsiro rudiki, asi vazhinji vachanamatira kwavari nekubata kumeso.
\v 35 Asi vamwe pane vanonzwisisa vachawa, kuvaedza nekuvanatsa, nekuvachenesa kusvika panguva yekupedzisira; nokuti pachava nenguva yakatarwa.
\p
\v 36 Zvino mambo achaita zvinoenderana nechido chake, uye achazvikudza, nekuzviita mukuru kupfuura mwari umwe neumwe, uye achataura zvinhu zvinoshamisa kupikisa Mwari wevamwari, uye achabudirira kusvika kutsamwa kwazadziswa, nokuti zvakatemwa zvichaitwa.
\v 37 Zvino haangarangariri Mwari wemadzibaba ake, kana chishuvo chevakadzi, kana kurangarira mwari upi neupi, nokuti achazvikudza kupfuura vese.
\v 38 Asi pachinzvimbo chake achakudza mwari wenhare zhinji; uye mwari madzibaba ake waasina kuziva achamukudza negoridhe, nesirivha, uye nemabwe anokosha, nezvinhu zvinodikanwa.
\v 39 Achaita saizvozvo panhare zhinji dzine simba namwari wevatorwa, waacharangarira achimuwedzera rumbidzo. Achaita kuti vatonge pamusoro pevazhinji, uye achagovera nyika nemutengo.
\p
\v 40 Zvino panguva yekupedzisira mambo wekuchamhembe achamusundidzira, namambo wekumaodzanyemba achauya kuzomurwisa sechamupupuri, ane ngoro nevatasvi vemabhiza nezvikepe zvizhinji. Zvino achapinda munyika idzo, uye achakukura ndokupfuura.
\v 41 Achapindawo munyika yakaisvonaka, uye zhinji dzichawa, asi idzi dzichapukunyuka paruoko rwake: Edhomu, neMoabhu, neyakanakisisa yevana vaAmoni.
\v 42 Achatandavadzirawo ruoko rwake pamusoro pedzinyika, uye nyika yeEgipita haingapukunyuki.
\v 43 Asi achava nesimba pamusoro pefuma yegoridhe neyesirivha, nepamusoro pezvinhu zvese zvinokosha zveEgipita; uye VaRibhia neVaItiyopiya vachava pamatsimba ake.
\v 44 Asi mashoko anobva kumabvazuva nekumaodzanyemba achamuvhundusa; naizvozvo achabuda nehasha kwazvo kunoparadza nekupedza chose vazhinji.
\v 45 Zvino achadzika matende emuzinda wake pakati pemakungwa pagomo rakaisvonaka dzvene; zvakadaro achasvika pakuguma kwake, uye haangavi nemubatsiri.